<!--
  Imprint (Impressum)

  Required by Swiss law for any website that provides a service.
  Identifies who operates the service and how to contact them.

  Note: The operator should fill in the actual address and contact
  details before going live. Placeholder values are marked with [brackets].
-->
<main class="container py-4">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8">

      <h1 class="mb-4">Imprint</h1>

      <!-- ── Operator ── -->
      <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Service Operator</h2>
      <address>
        <strong>Guillermo Pomphile</strong><br>
        [Street Address]<br>
        [Postal Code] [City]<br>
        Switzerland
      </address>

      <!-- ── Contact ── -->
      <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        <i class="bi bi-envelope"></i>
        Email: <a href="mailto:[your-email@example.com]">[your-email@example.com]</a>
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted small">
        Please use email for all enquiries regarding data protection,
        account deletion requests, or questions about the service.
      </p>

      <!-- ── Nature of the service ── -->
      <h2 class="h4 mt-4">About This Service</h2>
      <p>
        Quartier Bike ID is a <strong>private, non-commercial community project</strong>
        operated voluntarily for the neighbourhood. It is not a registered business
        and does not generate revenue.
      </p>
      <p>
        The garage parking contribution (CHF 40.00/year) is collected on behalf of
        the building community and is not income of the operator.
      </p>

      <!-- ── Technical details ── -->
      <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Technical Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Hosting:</strong> Self-hosted on a private Synology NAS in Switzerland</li>
        <li><strong>Public access:</strong> Via Cloudflare Tunnel (HTTPS encryption)</li>
        <li><strong>Domain:</strong> [bikes.yourdomain.com]</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- ── Data protection ── -->
      <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Data Protection</h2>
      <p>
        For information on how your personal data is processed, please see our
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        For data protection enquiries or to exercise your rights under the
        Swiss Federal Act on Data Protection (nDSG), please contact the
        operator using the email address above.
      </p>

      <!-- ── Disclaimer ── -->
      <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        The content of this website has been prepared with care. However, the
        operator assumes no liability for the accuracy, completeness, or
        timeliness of the information provided.
      </p>
      <p>
        This service is provided free of charge and without warranty.
        See the <a href="/terms">Terms of Use</a> for details.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</main>

